---
// ProcessSection コンポーネント - Modern Infographics Design
---

<section id="process" class="section-padding bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950/20">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="mb-6">
        サービスの流れ
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        シータ・クリニカル・サポートのシンプルな3ステップで研究支援を開始
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Desktop Layout -->
      <div class="hidden md:block">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Connection Lines -->
          <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl">
            <svg class="w-full h-8" viewBox="0 0 800 32" fill="none">
              <path d="M100 16 L300 16 M500 16 L700 16" stroke="hsl(var(--primary))" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="8 4" opacity="0.5"/>
              <!-- Arrows -->
              <polygon points="295,12 305,16 295,20" fill="hsl(var(--primary))" opacity="0.6"/>
              <polygon points="695,12 705,16 695,20" fill="hsl(var(--primary))" opacity="0.6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="text-center relative">
              <div class="relative mx-auto mb-8">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
                  <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    📋
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold shadow-lg">
                  1
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">お問い合わせ・ヒアリング</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">研究内容と参加者条件を詳しくお聞かせください</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="text-center relative">
              <div class="relative mx-auto mb-8">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 to-secondary/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
                  <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    🤖
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold shadow-lg">
                  2
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">AI分析・マッチング</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">条件に合致する参加者候補をAIが効率的に抽出</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="text-center relative">
              <div class="relative mx-auto mb-8">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/15 to-secondary/15 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
                  <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    🚀
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold shadow-lg">
                  3
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-foreground">サポート実施</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">翻訳、連絡、事務手続きを専門チームが代行</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Mobile Layout -->
      <div class="block md:hidden">
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
            <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold">
                  📋
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">
                1
              </div>
              <!-- Connecting line -->
              <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-0.5 h-12 bg-primary/30"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-foreground">お問い合わせ・ヒアリング</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">研究内容と参加者条件を詳しくお聞かせください</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
            <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 to-secondary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold">
                  🤖
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-6 h-6 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">
                2
              </div>
              <!-- Connecting line -->
              <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-0.5 h-12 bg-secondary/30"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-foreground">AI分析・マッチング</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">条件に合致する参加者候補をAIが効率的に抽出</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
            <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/15 to-secondary/15 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold">
                  🚀
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">
                3
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-foreground">サポート実施</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">翻訳、連絡、事務手続きを専門チームが代行</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>